title: The Boys
videoTitle: Season 3 Official Trailer | June 3 on Prime Video
videoDescription: Season 3 arrives June 3rd, only on Prime Video. Homelander is subdued. Butcher works for the government, supervised by Hughie of all people. But both men itch to turn this peace and quiet into blood and bone. So when The Boys learn of a mysterious anti-Supe weapon, it sends them crashing into The Seven, starting a war, and chasing the legend of the first Superhero: Soldier Boy.
